THE MANA WORLD
==============

 Version: 0.0.12    Date: 1/5/2005


 Development team:
  - See AUTHORS file for a list

 Powered by:

  - SDL, SDL_image, SDL_mixer (Media framework)
  - Guichan (GUI framework)
